%><h3>About Egyptian Hieroglyphs</h3>
<p>Egyptian Hieroglyphs are the ancient Egyptian writing system.</p>

<p>
The following table converts between the alphabet and Hieroglyphs.
Hieroglyphs without parentheses in the "Variant" column are converted one-way from Hieroglyph to Alphabet.
Hieroglyphs in parentheses are listed for reference only and are not converted.
</p>

